        "rstd",
        "gamma"
      ],
      "expr": "len(gamma.shape) <= len(dy.shape) and len(rstd.shape) == len(dy.shape) and rstd.shape[:len(dy.shape) - len(gamma.shape)] == dy.shape[:len(dy.shape) - len(gamma.shape)] and all((rstd.shape[i] == 1) or (rstd.shape[i] == dy.shape[i]) for i in range(len(dy.shape) - len(gamma.shape), len(dy.shape)))",
      "description": "rstd的shape需要以dy为基准满足broadcast关系，且非norm维与dy对应维度相同。",
      "source": "dy",
